                "181Ta(n,2n)180mTa, 206Pb(n,3n)204mPb are given"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CCW"
                ],
                "institute": "3INDAUW"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " 600 keV Cockcroft-Walton accelerator"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "\"Specpure\" metallic powders in the case of Ta and Hf",
                "and oxides of Gd, Yb, Pb with purity more than 99.9%",
                "were thoroughly mixed with aluminum powder discs",
                "of 3.3 cm diam. and 1 or 2 mm thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Deuteron on tritium. The neutron flux was of",
                "the order of 10**8 n/cm2/s, which was monitored by",
                "an auxiliary BF2 counter embedded in a paraffin block."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Calibrated using standard radioactive sources",
                "75Se, 133Ba, 152Eu. Self-absorption and scattering",
                "of gamma-rays were taken into account."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
